These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, milk, 7up, cola
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, r&b, salsa, techno
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, marigold, dahlia, zinnia
4 different pets are kept: frog, turtle, hedgehog, mouse
1. the person who growsmarigold is the fan of techno##1
2. the person who growsdahlia is between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking cola##2
3. the person who growsmarigold is the owner of the frog##1
4. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
5. the fan of metal is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
6. the owner of the hedgehog is the person drinking 7up##1
7. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
8. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far right##1
9. the person drinking milk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | milk | cola   | juice  | 7up  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b    | techno    | metal      | salsa    |
| Flower   | zinnia | marigold | dahlia | amaryllis |
| Pet     | mouse  | frog       | turtle    | hedgehog     |

