.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, singing, woodworking
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, february, september, june
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, bike, roller, quad-bike
4 different games are played: billiard, go, bridge, domino
1. the person playing domino is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is the person playing go##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
5. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person driving the roller and the person playing billiard##2
6. the person playing domino is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person driving the quad-bike##2
7. the person driving the bus is on the far right##1
8. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
9. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | woodworking | drawing    | singing  | cooking    |
| Birthday   | july      | february  | june  | september |
| Transport           | quad-bike      | roller       | bike      | bus       |
| Game         | go    | domino | bridge | billiard |

