.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, japanese, egyptian, malaysian
4 different pets are kept: snake, hedgehog, hamster, lizard
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, lawyer, paramedic, pilot
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, whist, snooker, chess
1. the paramedic is the person playing whist##1
2. the person playing whist is on the left of the pilot##1
3. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing whist##1
4. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
5. the egyptian is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
6. the lawyer is the owner of the lizard##1
7. the malaysian is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
8. the dutch is between the owner of the snake and the owner of the lizard##2
9. the owner of the hamster is between the egyptian and the lawyer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Nationality        | japanese | egyptian     | dutch   | malaysian     |
| Pet       | hedgehog   | snake   | hamster | lizard |
| Job         | analyst   | paramedic | pilot       | lawyer    |
| Game   | snooker    | whist | mah-jongg  | chess    |

