.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, italian, british, canadian
City: nizza, prague, san-francisco, london
4 different pets are kept: bird, frog, hamster, pony
There 4 different types of food: apricot, pear, zucchini, onion
 1. the person traveling to prague is on the far right##1
 2. the person traveling to london is the chinese##1
 3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person eating onion##1
 4. the person eating apricot is on the far left##1
 5. the person traveling to london is the owner of the frog##1
 6. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 7. the person traveling to prague is the british##1
 8. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
 9. the chinese is on the left of the person eating pear##1
10. the italian is between the owner of the bird and the canadian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Nationality           | chinese  | canadian | italian     | british |
| City   | london | nizza  | san-francisco | prague       |
| Pet           | frog       | pony    | hamster      | bird           |
| Food         | apricot | pear   | onion   | zucchini         |

