.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-5::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, dahlia, balloon-flower, amaryllis
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, lawyer, security-guard, social-worker
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, february, january, april
4 different pets are kept: horse, pony, rabbit, rat
 1. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 2. the owner of the horse is on the far left##1
 3. the security-guard is the person who growsdahlia##1
 4. the security-guard is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 6. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 7. the social-worker is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
 8. the lawyer is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 9. the person who growsballoon-flower is between the owner of the rat and the person who's birthday is in december##2
10. the person who's birthday is in january is the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Flower          | dahlia         | balloon-flower         | begonia     | amaryllis      |
| Job           | security-guard | social-worker | freelancer    | lawyer     |
| Birthday   | december      | january       | april    | february       |
| Pet         | horse     | rabbit       | rat | pony |

