The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, train, roller, van
House: ranch-style, gothic-revival, wooden, colonial
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, woodworking, writing, camping
1. the person driving the boat is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person driving the roller##2
2. the freelancer is between the person driving the boat and the colonial house##2
3. the wooden house is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the gothic-revival house##2
4. the librarian is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
5. the wooden house is the wooden house##1
6. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
7. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the analyst##1
8. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1
9. the person driving the train is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | librarian | freelancer | analyst  | paramedic |
| Transport   | train      | van       | boat     | roller      |
| House   | colonial   | gothic-revival      | wooden   | ranch-style   |
| Hobby         | writing   | camping    | filmmaking | woodworking   |

