 3. the fan of dubstep is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person eating cabbage##2
 4. the fan of metal is the person eating grapefruit##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person eating orange##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in november is the person eating pepper##1
 8. the fan of soul is on the far right##1
 9. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
10. the person who's birthday is in september is the person eating grapefruit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Sport   | tennis | weightlifting | water-polo  | rugby  |
| Music-Genre   | blues       | metal   | dubstep | soul    |
| Birthday   | november   | september   | january | march |
