 6. the person who growsdaisy is on the far left##1
 7. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
 8. the person who growsiris is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching comedy movies is between the person watching spy movies and the person who likes mauve##2
10. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |
