 7. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
 8. the owner of the turtle is between the person playing canasta and the person playing poker##2
 9. the person playing billiard is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
10. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person playing canasta and the person playing poker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
